reviewText: Good introduction to RVs, especially if you are new to RVs.  I was expecting more detailed information, however, from this fairly high priced DVD.

Informative for newbies/reseachers, however, I wouldn't order the 'Class A Motorhome 101 RV DVD' at the same time.  These two dvd's are totally identical except this one has bonus feature at the very end on gas efficiency!  Returned the other one, who needs 2 identical dvd's at $25 each!
The DVD is chock full of information for the beginner RV enthustiest. It goes through all the main systems with good ideas for all. A great informational DVD.
